<section>

<p>Load shedding operators provide the ability for SPL applications to temporarily discard tuples to reduce workload, for example an application may shed tuples in a low priority analytic flow to ensure high priority analytics have access to required cluster resources, during a peak in activity. 
</p>
</section>
<section>
  <title outputclass="splhead-1">Operators</title>
<sl>
